 <h3 id="toc1">Moon Upgrades</h3> 
 <p>Magic damage added; primarily modified by Magic stat. Requires Claymore +6 and <a class="wiki_link" title="Moonstone" href="/Moonstone">Moonstone</a>.</p> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
